Packages 
Package Description
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.client
This package contains all the classes associated to the ftp client management
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.main
This package contains all the classes for the runtime execution of the server
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.server
This package contains all the classes for the ftp requests, responses and also the FTP server management classes
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.server.request
This package contains all the classes for the ftp requests and ftp responses
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.server.request.control
This package contains all the classes for the ftp requests which can perform control commands on the connection
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.server.request.data
This package contains all the classes for the ftp requests which requires a data connection between the client and the server
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.tests
This package contains all unit test classes
fr.univ.lille1.ftp.util
This package contains all utility classes for the ftp server
